WELL DRIEN AND RESPECTABLE AND ON TIME

Passenger safety is not a priority for this platform. There is no guarantee that you will have a safe and smooth ride. Bolt as a platform does not ensure any safeguards or guarantees that the driver will begin the journey with the correct rider on board. Twice this week, there has been a random stranger in my ride. Bolt has yet to implement a robust confirmation system between driver and rider.
